==English==

===Etymology===
From Spanish ''[[frijoles refritos]]'' meaning “fried beans”, where ''[[re-]]'' adds emphasis

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[refried]] [[beans]]''' (''always plural'')

# A dry to mushy paste made by boiling, mashing{{,}} and then frying particularly [[pinto]] or [[black bean]]s, included in or served as anything from a main dish in Central America to a [[dip]] in the Southern U.S.